  • Reference

    Case types

    assuntos.Rd

    A dataset contains information about case types in Brazil.

    assuntos

    Format

    a data frame with 37022 lines and 15 variables.

    tribunal

    indicates which court is concerned

    ano

    subject year

    assunto_generico

    generic subject

    assunto_nome1

    first branch

    assunto_nome2

    second branch

    assunto_nome3

    third branch

    assunto_nome4

    fourth branch

    assunto_nome5

    fifth branch

    assunto_nome6

    sixth branch

    assunto_nome7

    seventh branch

    codigos

    code related to the subject

    assun_cod_inst

    instance codes

    x1_grau

    number of cases in first instance

    x2_grau

    number of cases in second instance

    juizado_especial

    number of cases in the special court

    turma_especial

    number of cases in the special class

    total

    total cases

    Source

    https://www.cnj.jus.br/
